N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 52.11 - Stipulations

State Regulations

Parties by agreement may stipulate as to any facts
involved in the proceedings. Such stipulation, to be effective, must be duly
noted in the stenographic record of the proceedings. Notes
